**Parent Settings (âš™ï¸ icon):**
- **Weather Location:**
  - Mode: "Automatic (IP-based)" or "Manual"
  - Automatic: Detect location via IP address (ip-api.com)
  - Manual: Search city name or enter coordinates
  - Shows current location and allows changing
- **Year View:**
  - Start month selection (Current/January/Custom month)
- **Calendar Sync:**
  - Sync calendar URL (webcal://)
  - Sync frequency (15/30/60 minutes)
  - Enable/disable sync
- **Display:**
  - Temperature unit (Celsius/Fahrenheit)
- **Categories:**
  - Category icon assignments
  - Special event categories for year view
- **Security:**
  - PIN code protection for settings
  - Enable/disable PIN

